text: The entire political class in the UK is worse than useless. Mad King George III would be an improvement.

Against indiscriminate and mass immigration in general. Immigration should be highly selective, and mostly separated from citizenship (i.e. limited to temporary residence). But very moderate absorption of  thoroughly-vetted high-quality people (including East and South Asians) is good.
Indeed. Catholic clergy are (quite correctly) not a protected class.
Russians worse behaved than I'd have guessed.
Only four times as criminal as native Norwegians.
... But compared to Somalis, they're angelic.
Vaguely disappointed by the Justin Castreau resignation. I was looking forward to his electoral humiliation.
